gomodel:SYNGO_1832  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.6 The ECD of IL-1RAcP and IL-1RAcPb bind the PTPδ ECD\n\nAuthors note:\n- Adhesion is measured in a cell aggregation assay on a sensor chip.\n- The referenced figures show adhesive properties in non-neuronal cells. The functional relevance for synapse formation between these pre- and postsynaptic proteins is represented in other tickets based on this paper.. Experimental description: - Overexpressed 1RAcP is of mouse species: \"The entire coding sequences of mouse IL-1RAcP, IL-1RAcPb, ...\"" ;
